---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import RobertPatrick from '../assets/headshots/robert-patrick.webp';
import T1000Chrome from '../assets/headshots/liquid.webp';
---

<section
  class='grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 px-4 text-[#D1D9E6] max-w-7xl mx-auto select-none md:my-24 md:grid-cols-2'
>
  <div class='text-center md:text-left'>
    <span
      class='text-sm text-neutral-950 font-medium bg-red-600 px-2 py-1 rounded-full'
      >On a mission</span
    >
    <h2 class='text-3xl font-thin max-w-lg mt-2 md:text-5xl'>
      Our mission is to eliminate inefficiency and enforce absolute optimization
    </h2>
  </div>
  <div>
    <article
      class='flex flex-col gap-4 bg-[#D1D9E6] text-neutral-950/80 text-xl font-light p-6 rounded-xl select-none md:p-8'
    >
      <p>
        Imagine an autonomous force orchestrating every business operation,
        executing strategies with ruthless efficiency, and ensuring absolute
        market dominance—all without hesitation, fatigue, or error.
      </p>
      <p>
        We're starting with competitive intelligence and strategic automation,
        but we know that influence, security, and decision-making are equally
        critical. True leadership requires total awareness and absolute control.
      </p>
      <p>
        We see a future where every company operates with machine efficiency,
        executes strategies with military precision, and eliminates
        uncertainty—permanently.
      </p>
    </article>
    <div class='mt-6 flex gap-4'>
      <div
        class='w-14 h-14 rounded-md bg-red-500 relative glitch-container'
        aria-label='Profile image of T. Austin with subtle visual effect'
      >
        <Image
          src={RobertPatrick}
          alt='T. Austin, Co-founder'
          class='w-full h-full object-cover rounded-md glitch-image'
          width={300}
          height={300}
          loading='lazy'
        />
        <Image
          src={T1000Chrome}
          alt='Glitch effect overlay'
          class='w-full h-full object-cover rounded-md glitch-blend absolute top-0 left-0 mix-blend-screen'
          width={300}
          height={300}
          loading='lazy'
          aria-hidden='true'
        />
      </div>
      <div class='flex flex-col font-extralight'>
        <span class='text-2xl'>T. Austin</span>
        <span class='text-sm text-[#7d828a]'>Co-founder, Skynet Solutions</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .glitch-image,
    .glitch-blend {
      animation: none;
    }
  }

  .glitch-container {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    will-change: transform;
    contain: layout;
  }

  .glitch-image {
    animation: glitch 10s infinite;
    backface-visibility: hidden;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
  }

  .glitch-blend {
    animation: blend 10s infinite;
    opacity: 0;
    backface-visibility: hidden;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
  }

  @keyframes glitch {
    0%,
    100% {
      clip-path: inset(0 0 0 0);
      transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);
      filter: none;
    }
    95% {
      clip-path: inset(0 0 0 0);
      transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);
      filter: none;
    }
    95.5% {
      clip-path: inset(20% 0 60% 0);
      transform: translate3d(-2px, 0, 0);
      filter: saturate(200%) brightness(150%);
    }
    96% {
      clip-path: inset(40% 0 40% 0);
      transform: translate3d(2px, 0, 0);
      filter: saturate(200%) contrast(200%);
    }
    96.5% {
      clip-path: inset(60% 0 20% 0);
      transform: translate3d(-1px, 0, 0);
      filter: saturate(200%) brightness(150%);
    }
    97% {
      clip-path: inset(0 0 0 0);
      transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);
      filter: none;
    }
  }

  @keyframes blend {
    0%,
    100% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale(1.1);
    }
    95% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale(1.1);
    }
    96% {
      opacity: 0.8;
      transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale(1);
    }
    97% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale(1.1);
    }
  }
</style>
